{"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[0, 4]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"symbolPlacement","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Otherwise, it is ignored.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of th